### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login to get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### 2. Get all contacts (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get all contacts (sorted by name descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts?page=1&pageSize=50&sortBy=name_desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get contact by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts/CONTACT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Create a new contact
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "田中太郎",
  "address": "東京都渋谷区",
  "phoneNumber": "03-1234-5678"
}

### 6. Create contact with minimal data (name only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "山田花子"
}

### 7. Update a contact
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts/CONTACT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "田中太郎",
  "address": "東京都新宿区",
  "phoneNumber": "03-9876-5432"
}

### 8. Delete a contact
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts/CONTACT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Test validation - empty name (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "",
  "address": "東京都"
}

### 10. Test validation - invalid phone number (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "テストユーザー",
  "phoneNumber": "invalid-phone"
}

### 11. Test validation - name too long (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "あああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああ"
}

### 12. Test duplicate name (should fail on second attempt)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "重複テスト"
}
